quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  45,27,"“Ndipo ufumu wa kumwamba ndi pansi ngwa Allah, ndipo tsiku limene Qiyâma idzachitika, (anthu) ogwirizana ndi zonama adzaonongeka patsikulo"
  45,28,"“Ndipo udzaliona gulu lililonse litagwada (uku nkhope zili zyoli); gulu lililonse lidzaitanidwa ku kaundula wake (kukamuwerenga): “Lero mulipidwa zimene mudali kuchita!”"
  45,29,““Uyu kaundula Wathu akunena zoona za inu; ndithu Ife tidali kulemba zimene mudali kuchita.”
  45,30,"“Koma amene adakhulupirira ndi kuchita zabwino, Mbuye wawo adzawalowetsa ku chifundo Chake; kumeneko ndiko kupambana koonekera"
  45,31,"“Ndipo amene adakanira, (adzauzidwa kuti): “Kodi Ayah Zanga sizidali kuwerengedwa kwa inu? Koma inu mudadzikweza; ndipo mudali anthu oipa.”"
  45,32,"“Ndipo kukanenedwa kuti lonjezo la Allah ndiloona, ndikuti Qiyâma ilibe chikaiko, mudali kunena: “Sitikudziwa Qiyâma kuti nchiyani; tikungoganizira chabe, ndipo tilibe chitsimikizo (cha Kiyamayo).”"
  45,33,"“Choncho, kuipa kwa zimene adachita kudzawaonekera, ndipo zidzawazinga zimene ankazichitira chipongwe"
  45,34,"“Kudzanenedwanso kwa iwowa: “Lero tikuiwalani (pokusiyani mchilango) monga momwe inu mudaiwalira kukumana ndi tsiku lanu ili. Ndipo malo anu ndi ku Moto, ndipo mulibe wokupulumutsani.”"
  45,35,"““Zimenezi nchifukwa chakuti inu mudazichitira chipongwe Ayah za Allah, ndipo moyo wa pa dziko udakunyengani.” Choncho lero satulutsidwa mmenemo ndipo madandaulo awo savomerezedwa"
  45,36,"“Tero kutamandidwa konse ndi kwa Allah, Mbuye wakumwamba ndi Mbuye wa pa dziko lapansi; Mbuye wazolengedwa"
  45,37,"“Ndipo ukulu ndi Wake, kumwamba ndi pansi; ndipo Iye ndi Wamphamvu zoposa, Wanzeru zakuya"